{"type": "article", "id": 24935, "title": "数字灯丝钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-05T07:03:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607124742au6zRE0TjmVSMx1n.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一盏非常酷炫的数字钟，它是用亮灯的形式来指示时间。4 个椭圆形的玻璃罩里用灯丝拼出了从 0 到 9 的数字形状，每到相应的时间就会点亮相应的灯，隐隐像一团燃烧的火焰，适合放在酒吧等环境中。它也可以作为夜灯使用。有枫木和花梨木两种外壳，分别售价 235 美元、285 美元，<a href=\"http://www.ckie.com/products/nixie-clocks#.VwJ00sdhyS8\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124739FrfSAwMTmpU2sBWC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124739qYbJ7fOuwIsElCzH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124740S0QqiMptxsJPvbn1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124740misH2WXrTdBcP0A5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124741bWYmMVHRXqheJOjv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}